sources.description:
A young alien and a teenage earthling fall in love, and plot to stop the alien's race from using Earth as a food-breeding ground for giant lobsters from their planet.

Colorized version https://youtu.be/8M_epWZz7lM
Director: Tom Graeff
Writer: Tom Graeff
Stars: David Love, Dawn Bender, Bryan Grant
Genre:  Classics, Cult Movies, Horror, Science Fiction & Fantasy
